      • create

        public static SQLExpression<java.lang.Number> create(AppContext conn,
                                     SQLExpression<?> a,
                                     Operator op,
                                     SQLExpression<?> b)
        A factory method for binary SQLExpressions. Usually this will return a BinaryExpression but may return some other expression as a result of on-the-fly simplification if the AppContext parameter is non-null and the appropriate feature is turned on.
        Parameters:
        conn - AppContext used to read config, null suppresses simplification
        a - SQLExpression first argument
        op - Operator to apply
        b - SQLExpression second argument.
        Returns:
        SQLExpression
